Class ResultSet<T extends IResult>

java.lang.Object
  de.topicmapslab.tmql4j.components.processor.results.ResultSet<T>

CTMResult, SimpleResultSet, XMLResult
public abstract class ResultSet<T extends IResult>
extends java.lang.Object
implements IResultSet<T>

Base implementation of IResultSet to implement the method providing base functionality. The result set represents a 2-dimension container containing a number of IResults. functionality.

Author:
Sven Krosse
